THE STATE OF FLORIDA, ex rel. JOE MUNN, v. JIMMY SULLIVAN, as Sheriff of Dade County, Florida. 23 So. (2nd) 717

June Term, 1945

November 20, 1945 Division B G. A. Worley, Jack Kehoe and Lawrence A. Truett, for appellant. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General, and Reeves Bowen and Cecil T. Barrington, Assistant Attorneys General, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

Judgment below affirmed.

CHAPMAN, C. J., BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
